    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nAny key strokes the navigate the help switch focus to the error buffer showing the error below, rending the help buffer useless as it cannot be explored\r\n\r\n```\r\nError in decoration provider treesitter/highlighter.win:\r\nError executing lua: ...d-0.10.0/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter/query.lua:252: Query error\r\nat 58:2. Invalid node type \"modeline\":\r\n(modeline) @keyword.directive\r\n ^\r\n\r\nstack traceback:\r\n        [C]: in function '_ts_parse_query'\r\n        ...d-0.10.0/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter/query.lua:252: in function 'fn'\r\n        ...pped-0.10.0/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/func/_memoize.lua:58: in function 'fn'\r\n        ...pped-0.10.0/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/func/_memoize.lua:58: in function 'get'\r\n        ....0/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter/highlighter.lua:28: in function 'new'\r\n        ....0/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter/highlighter.lua:240: in function 'get_query'\r\n        ....0/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter/highlighter.lua:188: in function 'fn'\r\n        ...0/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter/languagetree.lua:491: in function 'for_each_tre\r\ne'\r\n        ....0/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter/highlighter.lua:175: in function 'prepare_high\r\nlight_states'\r\n        ....0/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesi\r\n```\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nnvim --clean +help\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nIf errors during rendering of help pages occur the errors are only displayed once or are shown in a manner where the keyboard focus is kept on the original buffer\n\n### Neovim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.10.0 Build type: Release LuaJIT 2.1.1693350652\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nno, vim 9.0.2136\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nProductName:            macOS ProductVersion:         14.4.1 BuildVersion:           23E224\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\ntmux 3.4 running in alacritty 0.13.2\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nalacritty\n\n### Installation\n\nnixpkgs",
